events.name: ゴブリン討伐　ラスト

parameters:
\n< Serena >...I can't find anything. Is it just my
imagination...?

\n< Serena >Wha... what... a green, baby... is it a goblin
hatchling? This...
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Ag... Agigi...

\n< Serena >U-uhh... w-what...! What is this... just looking
at it... makes my heart flutter...!
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Gee...!
\n< Serena >N-No...!

\n< Serena >Haah... I ended up running away without
thinking...

\n< Serena >Even though it's supposed to be a powerless
infant, just because it has a shape
similar to a human, it feels so
grotesque...
\n< Serena >Extermination... is... it okay...? Only one of them won't last long anyway.
\n< Serena >I mean, I don't want to go back to the cabin......

\n< Serena >However, if I don't have any proof of
extermination this time, Master will get
angry at me again...
\n< Serena >No, I tried. Mm.
\n< Serena >No, I tried. Mm.
\n< Guild Master >Yes...yes. I knew you would....

\n< Serena >Y-Yes. With this, there are only \V[2501] more
left.

"  I've completed the goblin subjugation.
Let's go back to the inn and rest."
"  I cleared the quest."
回想セーブ Goblin Defeat at Hot Springs Town
\n< Serena >Hm, mmm... huh!?
\n< Goblin >Gye! Gyiii!
\n< Serena >Huh!?
\n< Serena >W-What... is this situation...!?

\n< Serena >(I've been taken to their nest...? Being
restrained by goblins... There are
roughly seven of them around me...)

\n< Serena >I have the ring... If only I could create
an Affabel...
\n< Goblin >Gya!
\n< Serena >Stop it! Don't pull on it!!
\n< Serena >Stop, stop--
\n< Goblin >Gya!

\n< Serena >Uwaaa!? M-My clothes...!? L-Let go! Don't
look!!

\n< Serena >(Oh... my focus... is disrupted...!
To be thrown off by something like this...
I can't regenerate my equipment...!)
\n< Goblin >Giggle giggle...
\n< Serena >Haa, haa...?
\n< Serena >!?... W-What are you rubbing against me?!
\n< Serena >Disgusting...! No...!
\n< Goblin >Gyuhee... Gihh...
\n< Serena >Huh...!?
\n< Serena >Ah...uh...a...!

\n< Serena >What... this isn't an attack... what are they
doing to me... what is the goblin
doing...?
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
\n< Goblin >....

\n< Serena >Stop... don't bring that near me... it's
 very disgusting...!
\n< Serena >(Like something you're not supposed to see...!)
\n< Serena >Get away! Don't... stop... ah!
\n< Serena >Yaaaaaaaah!?
\n< Serena >No! No! Not there...!
\n< Serena >It's pushing...! Huh!? No...!
\n< Goblin >Ghehehe... Ghi!

エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1

\n< Erika >Oorara! You goblins! Making a ruckus in broad
daylight!
\n< Serena >Ah... Erika-dono...!?

\n< Erika >Oh? Hey, who do I see? It's Serena, isn't
it!
\n< Erika >Geez, talk about a close call!
\n< Erika >Fine, I guess I have no choice!You owe me a favor!
\n< Erika >Ahh, these goblins are so slimy...!
\n< Erika >Serena, are you okay?

\n< Serena >I'm fine. I'm sorry, Erika-done...
Thank you.

\n< Erika >Be careful. Even weaklings have the power
to kill humans.
\n< Serena >It really hit me.

\n< Erika >Oh. Well, let's go home...
Wait you can't do that with that outfit on,
 can you?

\n< Erika >I'll go look for some clothes or fabric that
you can wear.
\n< Serena >I'm sorry...
\n< Serena >*sigh*...
\n< Serena >What... was that, I wonder...
\n< Serena >I was scared...

\n< Serena >It's not about pain or
death or anything like that.

\n< Serena >It feels like a dream. I don't think I'll
be able to forget it for a while...
Scene_Recollection.prototype.rngd_exit_scene();

\n< Guild Master >It seems like you had quite an experience,
Erika.
\n< Serena >Well... I'm ashamed to admit it.

\n< Guild Master >How about it? Aren't you tired of being an
adventurer? It's painful, it's
disgusting, and on top of that, it
stinks.
\n< Serena >....
\n< Serena >No, it's fine.

\n< Serena >Indeed, there is fear. There were also aspects
that I underestimated.

\n< Serena >However, there is something I must do from now
on. So, I will move forward. There is no
choice but to continue.
\n< Guild Master >Tch.

\n< Guild Master >Well... for now, since the goblins are gone,
the request is considered complete.

\n< Guild Master >Here, your reward. Go to sleep, eat, and take
a bath quickly.
\n< Serena >....
\n< Serena >...This makes it \V[2501] more to go.
"  It was a close call, but I managed to complete."
"  I'll go home and rest for today."
"I lost to a goblin."
